<item>
            <title>[PIG-3576] NPE due to PIG-3549 when job never gets submitted</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-3576</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;NPE can happen if job never gets submitted due to errors like - input path does not exists. Following line (toString method) throws npe-&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;msg.append(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;JobID: &quot;&lt;/span&gt; + j.getAssignedJobID().toString() + &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot; Reason: &quot;&lt;/span&gt; + j.getMessage());
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Apparently, a.toString can throw NPE, but String.valueOf(a) handles null well(writes &quot;null&quot; for null values).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
